I"#<h1 id="assembly-and-annotation-collection">Assembly and Annotation Collection</h1>

<p>This workflow can assemble and annotate multiple genomes in one submission.  The results from one submission will be packaged together into a single file.  The workflow uses the <a href="https://github.com/tseemann/shovill/">shovill</a> and <a href="http://www.vicbioinformatics.com/software.prokka.shtml">Prokka</a> software for assembly and annotation of genomes, respectively, as well as <a href="http://quast.sourceforge.net/quast.html">QUAST</a> for assembly quality assessment.  The specific Galaxy tools are listed in the table below.</p>

<table>
  <thead>
